data.description: DOUBLE LOT all in one parcel. Purchase from the original owner! This well-maintained contemporary and spacious two-bedroom offers open living with cathedral ceiling, brick fireplace, versatile open loft, functional laundry with storage, two full baths. Kitchen has loads of counters and cabinets with island and appliances. Open living room, dining, and kitchen area. Fantastic heated attached garage with two separate storage sheds. All this on an extra wide double lot! Updates include Roof and Siding (3yrs), Hot Water Tank (2023), Whole House Generator (8yrs), Stackable Washer/Dryer (2months), faucets, fixtures, flooring, tiles and much more. Just a few minutes from Houghton Lake! Quick access to major roadways and expressways.
